OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FUnsettled
OL,6,Fwith rain for many on Friday. Brighter
OL,7,Fbut with some showers on Saturday,
OL,8,Fbefore cloud and rain returns from the
OL,9,Fwest on Sunday. Often windy,
OL,10,Fespecially in the west.
